,966 km of the line that exists today. ', 'The railway companies operating on the network were nationalized in 1948 with the creation of the state railroad corporation Ferrocarriles Argentinos.\n', 'The train runs between Cape Town to Johannesburg. A high-speed rail network has been proposed in the country but the work is yet to begin.\n', ' The country has one of the best networks in the world'),
