ods. ', '                        \r\nAcross from Lake Geneva, this upscale hotel dating from 1875 is a minute\'s walk from the nearest ferry stop, 8 minutes on foot from Geneva train station and 1 km from the Jet d\'Eau.\r\n', '                            \r\nA 2-minute walk from Place VendÃ´me square, this luxe hotel sits among upscale shops in the 2nd arrondissement. It\'s a 7-minute walk from Palais Garnier opera house.\r\n', '                           \r\nFour Seasons Hotel George V is a luxury hotel on avenue George V in the 8th arrondissement of Paris. A-lister worth their salt can miss a shot of themselves entering its gilded art deco doors after a day spent shopping in the Golden Triangle. \r\n', 'thegrandresortlagonissi.jpg', 'palms.jpg', 'fourseasonaustralia.jpg', 'presidentwilsonhotel.jpg', 'stay-atlantis-paradise-island.jpg', 'ritzcarlton.jpg', 'alarab.jpg', 'lerichemond.jpg', 'parkhayatt.jpg', 'fourseasons.webp', 'TRAVELS', '   the grand resort lagonissi, greece  ($35K -$48k)', ' palm casino resort hotel, las vegas ($30K-$36k)', ' four seasons hotel, new york ($27K-$32k)', '    president wilson hotel ($25K-$30k) geneva switzerland', '   Atlantis resort hotel ($25500)', '   ritz carlton ($24000) ,tokyo', '     hotel al Arab Dubai (23000$)', '    le richemond 17500$', '  park Hyatt, Paris ($15000)', '  four seasons hotel geroge v  ($15000)', '                       Room service is available 24/7. Breakfast is complimentary, and there are 7 restaurants, including a poolside cafe, 2 eateries with sea views, and 2 terrace lounge bars. ', '                           Other amenities include 2 tennis courts, an outdoor pool, and a kids\' club, as well as a luxe spa, a cinema, and a private beach with water sports.\r\n      ', '                            Suites add kitchens, separate living rooms, and/or private lanais with hot tubs. A free shuttle to the Strip is offered. Dining options include an upmarket steakhouse, an Italian eatery, and a sophisticated Fr